commentPostTextItems.html: South Africa have won this match very convincingly with a huge margin of 171 runs and with this they win the series 3-0. Boucher adjudged both Man-of-match and Man-of-series. Thats it from us. Cheers and bye!

milestones.description: Mark Boucher has broken the record for most sixes in an innings (10) in ODIs for SA, going past Cullinan's 7
This is the highest match aggregate (665) involving teams South Africa & Zimbabwe in ODIs

stories.title: Smith impressed by South African onslaught
stories.subTitle: South Africa v Zimbabwe, 3rd ODI, Potchefstroom
stories.seoTitle: Smith impressed by South African onslaught
stories.summary: South Africa's Mark Boucher-led run riot against Zimbabwe at Potchefstroom yesterday has left Graeme Smith, a spectator in the crowd, very impressed

stories.title: Boucher blitz blows Zimbabwe away
stories.subTitle: South Africa v Zimbabwe, 3rd ODI, Potchefstroom
stories.summary: Mark Boucher's brutal 147 off 68 balls powerd South Africa to 418 for 5 in the final ODI at Potchefstroom. In reply Zimbabwe scored 247 for 4 as South Africa swept the series 3-0
